aragon-ai (1.1.10) stable; urgency=low

  * LLM Integration: The LLM prompt was replaced to support a "playlist" media_type and to extract a "room" parameter from user queries.
  * Playlist Functionality: Full support for "playlist" media type was added, including schema updates, 
    output cleaning, and a new Spotify playlist search function with fuzzy matching and error handling.
  * Query Preprocessing: User queries are now cleaned by removing "spotify" and "on spotify" (case-insensitive) before LLM processing.
  * Room Handling: Room detection was enhanced. The system now prioritizes a "room" from the LLM response. If not present,
    it uses the siteId from the request. Room validation uses fuzzy matching against actual Sonos rooms for robustness.
  * Artist Search: The Spotify artist search was significantly improved by fetching more candidates, trying exact matches first,
    then using more reliable fuzzy matching, and increasing the matching threshold.

 -- root <jens@proknx.com>  Wed, 27 May 2025 12:00:00 +0100

